#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Simplify your finances with the seamlessly integrated <strong>Accounting</"
"strong> app."
msgstr ""
"Forenkl din økonomi med den problemfrit integrerede <strong>Regnskabsapp</"
"strong>."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Since you are using the integrated website, your contact form is configured "
"to automatically create an opportunity. <br/>\n"
"            A customer has filled it in and is inquiring about the "
"possibility of a Family Dive - how exciting! This section will take you "
"through all the steps to turn this request into a sale.<br/>\n"
"            First we open the <strong>CRM</strong>-App. There we see the new "
"request in the stage New."
msgstr ""
"Da du bruger den integrerede hjemmeside, er din kontaktformular konfigureret "
"til automatisk at oprette en salgsmulighed.<br/>\n"
"En kunde har udfyldt formularen og forhører sig om en familiedykning – hvor "
"spændende! Dette afsnit guider dig gennem alle trinene til at omdanne "
"forespørgslen til et salg.<br/>\n"
"Først åbner vi <strong>CRM</strong>-appen. Her ser vi den nye forespørgsel i "
"fasen Ny."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Some customers might spontaneously decide to join you for a tour or an "
"event, instead of booking online in advance. This is where the POS-App "
"shines, which allows your customer to simply pay on the spot and join the "
"fun."
msgstr ""
"Nogle kunder vælger måske spontant at deltage i en udflugt eller et "
"arrangement i stedet for at booke online på forhånd. Her kommer POS-appen "
"ind i billedet, så kunderne nemt kan betale på stedet og straks komme i gang."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Store and organize client information in the <strong>Contacts </strong>app."
msgstr "Gem og organisér kundeoplysninger i appen <strong>Kontakter </strong>."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Streamline billing and financial management with the <strong>Invoicing app</"
"strong>."
msgstr ""
"Strømlin fakturering og økonomistyring med <strong>Faktureringsappen</strong>"
"."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Streamline team management and integrate employees into every process using "
"the <strong>Employees</strong> app."
msgstr ""
"Optimér teamadministrationen og integrér medarbejderne i alle processer med "
"<strong>Medarbejderappen</strong>."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.contact_us
msgid "Submit"
msgstr "Send"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>CRM App</strong> manages all customer relations, helps you keep "
"track of leads and website visitors and increase your sales."
msgstr ""
"<strong>CRM-appen</strong> administrerer alle kunderelationer, hjælper med "
"at følge op på leads og besøgende på hjemmesiden og øger omsætningen."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>POS App</strong> allows you to handle payments for walk-in "
"customers."
msgstr ""
"<strong>POS-appen</strong> giver dig mulighed for at håndtere betalinger for "
"kunder, der kommer ind i butikken."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <strong>Website App </strong>serves as your company's calling card, "
"allows customers to contact you and even purchase their aquatic adventures "
"from anywhere in the world."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Hjemmesideappen </strong>fungerer som dit firmas visitkort og giver "
"kunderne mulighed for at kontakte dig og booke deres vandaktiviteter over "
"hele verden."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Customer field is <strong>not</strong> required on the opportunity form."
msgstr ""
"Feltet Kunde er <strong>ikke</strong> påkrævet i salgslejemålsformularen."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The final step in this flow is for us to reserve the relevant resource to "
"ensure we don't get double booked - in the case our diving expedition it is "
"our boat.<br/>\n"
"            To do so, we go to the <strong>Appointments-App</strong>, select "
"<strong>Schedule </strong>and<strong> Resources Bookings. </strong>Then we "
"click on the agreed upon date and fill the necessary information in the "
"form\n"
"            <strong>.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"Det sidste trin i denne proces er at reservere den relevante ressource for "
"at sikre, at vi ikke bliver dobbeltbooket – i vores dykkerekspedition er det "
"båden.<br/>\n"
"            For at gøre dette går vi til <strong>Aftalerapp</strong>, vælger "
"<strong>Planlægning</strong> og <strong>Ressourcebookinger</strong>. "
"Derefter klikker vi på den aftalte dato og udfylder de nødvendige "
"oplysninger i formularen<strong>.</strong>"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr ""
"De er alle inkluderet i dit nuværende abonnement. Gå straks på opdagelse i "
"dem! 🙃"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:appointment.resource,description:outdoor_activities.appointment_resource_1
msgid "This is our trusty ship"
msgstr "Dette er vores trofaste skib"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This package is ideal for any outdoor activity provider - from scuba diving "
"to paragliding. Whether you want to reach out to customers, offer regular "
"experiences or certification courses - This guide will help you manage\n"
"            your business more efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Denne pakke er ideel for alle udbydere af udendørsaktiviteter – fra dykning "
"til paragliding. Uanset om du ønsker at nå ud til kunder, tilbyde "
"regelmæssige oplevelser eller certificeringskurser, hjælper denne vejledning "
"dig med at administrere\n"
"            din virksomhed mere effektivt."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To be able to sell tickets for your events via your website, you need to go "
"to<strong> Events -&gt; Configuration </strong>first and activate the "
"feature <strong>Online Ticketing.<br/></strong>To allow the integration\n"
"                    of this flow with the <strong>Sales-App</strong>, you "
"also need to activate<strong> Tickets with Sale</strong>."
msgstr ""
"For at kunne sælge billetter til dine arrangementer online via din "
"hjemmeside skal du først gå til <strong>Arrangementer &gt; Indstillinger</"
"strong> og aktivere funktionen <strong>Online billetsalg</strong>.<br/>\n"
"For at sikre, at processen\n"
"                    fungerer problemfrit sammen med <strong>Salgsappen</"
"strong>, skal du også aktivere <strong>Billetter med salg</strong>."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid "To be sure to stay updated, follow us on"
msgstr "Følg os for at holde dig opdateret"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To ensure that your POS is set up correctly, we strongly recommend following "
"the step-by-step guide from our official documentation, which you can find "
"linked below:<br/>\n"
"                    <br/>"
msgstr ""
"For at sikre korrekt konfiguration af dit kassesystem anbefaler vi, at du "
"nøje følger den trinvise vejledning i vores officielle dokumentation, som er "
"tilgængelig via nedenstående link:<br/>\n"
"                    <br/>"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To get started on our first event, we need to go to the <strong>Events-App </"
"strong>and click on <strong>New</strong>. In the following form, we can set "
"up all the key information, such as the date and duration of the event, the\n"
"            location and whether there is a limited number of participants. "
"<br/>"
msgstr ""
"For at oprette vores første begivenhed går vi til <strong>"
"Arrangementerappen</strong> og klikker på <strong>Ny</strong>. I den "
"efterfølgende formular kan vi indtaste alle vigtige oplysninger, såsom dato, "
"varighed,\n"
"            sted og om deltagerantallet er begrænset. <br/>"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model:website.menu,name:outdoor_activities.website_menu_4
msgid "Top Menu for Website 1"
msgstr "Hovedmenu for hjemmeside 1"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the<strong> Sales App</strong> to validate orders and create custom "
"quotations for special VIP bookings."
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong>Salgsappen</strong> til at godkende ordrer og oprette "
"brugerdefinerede tilbud til VIP-specialbookinger."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid "Welcome to the <strong>Odoo Outdoor Activities Package!</strong>"
msgstr "Velkommen til <strong>Odoos pakke til udendørs aktiviteter!</strong>"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:outdoor_activities.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "Velkommen! God fornøjelse med at gå på opdagelse."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model:crm.tag,name:outdoor_activities.crm_tag_8
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.contact_us
msgid "Whatsapp"
msgstr "WhatsApp"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With the <strong>Events App</strong> you can create certification courses "
"and special Experiences for your customers."
msgstr ""
"Med <strong>Arrangementerappen</strong> kan du oprette certificeringskurser "
"og skabe unikke oplevelser for dine kunder."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With the <strong>Surveys</strong> app you can gather valuable customer "
"feedback and business insights to offer your customers the best experience "
"possible"
msgstr ""
"Med <strong>Spørgeundersøgelserappen</strong> kan du indhente værdifuld "
"kundefeedback og forretningsindsigt, så du kan give dine kunder den bedst "
"mulige oplevelse"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With the Outdoor Activities-Package you can offer regular experiences that "
"your customers can conveniently book online. In our sample database, we "
"offer diving outings on our trusty ship Deep Blue Something. As everyone of "
"our\n"
"            expeditions requires our ship to get to the diving spot, our "
"first step is to set up our ship. We do this by going to the "
"<strong>Appointments-app </strong>and under <strong>Configuration</strong> "
"selecting\n"
"            <strong>Resources</strong>. <br/>\n"
"            There we click on <strong>New</strong>. Since we want several "
"guests on the same tour, we set this resource to <strong>shareable</strong> "
"and set the <strong>capacity </strong>to the 10 seats we have on our boat - "
"this\n"
"            means that we can have up to 10 participants per tour.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"Med pakken til udendørs aktiviteter kan du tilbyde regelmæssige oplevelser, "
"som dine kunder nemt kan booke online. I vores eksempeldatabase tilbyder vi "
"dykkerture på vores trofaste skib Deep Blue Something. Da alle vores\n"
"            udflugter kræver, at skibet sejler til dykkerstedet, starter vi "
"med at konfigurere skibet. Det gør vi ved at gå til <strong>Aftalerappen</"
"strong> og under <strong>Konfiguration</strong> vælge \n"
"            <strong>Ressources</strong>.<br/>\n"
"            Her klikker vi på <strong>Ny</strong>. Da vi ønsker at have "
"flere gæster på samme tur, indstiller vi ressourcen til <strong>delbare</"
"strong> og sætter <strong>kapacitet</strong> til de 10 pladser, vi har på "
"båden – hvilket\n"
"            betyder, at vi kan have op til 10 deltagere pr. tur.<br/>"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or explore more features?"
msgstr ""
"Vil du gerne tale med os om dit Odoo-setup eller drøfte nogle spørgsmål mere "
"detaljeret?"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.ir_ui_view_3241
msgid ""
"You are ensured through DAN during the entirety of the course. All dives, "
"equipment and emergencies are included. Please find more information on the "
"exact coverage&amp;nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"Du er forsikret gennem DAN under hele kurset. Alle dyk, udstyr og "
"nødsituationer er dækket. Du kan finde yderligere oplysninger om det præcise "
"dækningsomfang&amp;nbsp;"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Du kan tilgå alle installerede apps i din Odoo-database direkte fra "
"hoveddashboardet."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can also create a Reservation Fee or Down-Payment and link it to the "
"Appointment Type, if you prefer your customers to only pay partially upon "
"booking."
msgstr ""
"Du kan også konfigurere et tilmeldingsgebyr eller et depositum og knytte det "
"til Aftalerappen, hvis du ønsker, at dine kunder kun betaler et delbeløb ved "
"booking."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can still do it after installation by upgrading your package in Apps."
msgstr "Du kan fortsat gøre dette ved at opdatere din pakke via Apps."

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:outdoor_activities.homepage
msgid ""
"Your Dynamic Snippet will be displayed here... This message is displayed "
"because you did not provide both a filter and a template to use.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"Dit dynamiske kodestykke vises her ... Denne meddelelse vises, fordi du ikke "
"har angivet både et filter og en skabelon, som skal anvendes.<br/>"

#. module: outdoor_activities
#: model_terms:event.event,description:outdoor_activities.event_event_3
